frames.caption: A dark figure stands atop a building overlooking a sprawling cityscape illuminated by countless lights. Lightning strikes in the distance, casting a dramatic glow over the scene. The rain pours down, adding to the moody atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a vigilante figure standing on a rooftop in a rain-soaked city at night. The city is bustling with lights, and a lightning bolt illuminates the sky, creating a dramatic and tense atmosphere.

frames.caption: A lone figure in a dark cape stands on a rooftop, overlooking a sprawling cityscape illuminated by countless lights. Lightning strikes in the distance, casting a dramatic glow over the scene. The atmosphere is tense and foreboding, with rain adding to the moody ambiance.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dark, rainy night in a bustling city. A caped figure stands vigilantly on a rooftop, surveying the city below as lightning illuminates the sky.
